archimate:BusinessObject.name: Accepted system or system element
archimate:BusinessObject.documentation: System element or system is transferred from supplier to acquirer and the product or service is available to the project

properties.value: Laut INCOSE Handbuch 4.0 - übersetzt von GfSE: "Ein abgenommenes System oder - Systemelement entspricht einem vom Zulieferer an den Beschaffer übergebenen System oder Systemelement, das dann dem Projekt zur Verfügung steht."
System element or system is transferred from supplier to acquirer and the product or service is available to the project
